    public final class Saml10SuccessResponseView
extends NoSamlNamespaceAbstractSaml10ResponseView
    A replacement implementation for the Saml10SuccessResponseView that inheits its configuration from NoSamlNamespaceAbstractSaml10ResponseView so as to override the behavior that generates SAML namespaces for a successful SAML assertion.
    Since:
    1.7
    Author:
    Misagh Moayyed
